---
---

<section id="opensource-feed" class="bg-dark px-4 py-20 border-t border-emerald-400/10">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-white">
      开源<span class="text-emerald-400">热点周报</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-400 mb-4">由 GitHub Scout Agent 自动追踪的最具潜力的开源项目</p>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">最后更新：2026年4月12日</p>
    <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-emerald-400 mx-auto mb-16"></div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- 开源项 1 -->
      <article class="group p-6 border-l-2 border-emerald-400/30 hover:border-emerald-400 transition-colors hover:bg-dark/50">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">
            🧠 awesome-persona-distill-skills：AI Agent 人格化技能集合
          </h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap ml-4">⭐ 3.3k</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
          汇集了基于特定人物、关系和场景的 AI Agent 技能，展示了 AI Agent 人格化和情境化的巨大潜力。为特定行业开发高度专业化的 Agent 技能，是蓝海市场。
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://github.com/xixu-me/awesome-persona-distill-skills" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-emerald-400 text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 开源项 2 -->
      <article class="group p-6 border-l-2 border-emerald-400/30 hover:border-emerald-400 transition-colors hover:bg-dark/50">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">
            🚀 hermes-agent-orange-book：Hermes Agent 框架实战指南
          </h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap ml-4">⭐ 2.0k</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
          关于 Nous Research 开源 AI Agent 框架 Hermes 的实战指南，提供从入门到精通的 Agent 构建完整路径。
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://github.com/alchaincyf/hermes-agent-orange-book" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-emerald-400 text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub →</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 开源项 3 -->
      <article class="group p-6 border-l-2 border-emerald-400/30 hover:border-emerald-400 transition-colors hover:bg-dark/50">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">
            💡 gemma-tuner-multimodal：Apple Silicon 本地微调大模型
          </h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 whitespace-nowrap ml-4">⭐ 1.2k</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-3">
          在 Apple Silicon 上使用 PyTorch + Metal Performance Shaders 对 Gemma 4 模型进行多模态（音频/图像/文本）微调，大幅降低个人开发者进行大模型优化的门槛。
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://github.com/mattmireles/gemma-tuner-multimodal" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-emerald-400 text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub →</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a href="/opensource" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 border-2 border-emerald-400 text-emerald-400 hover:bg-emerald-400 hover:text-dark transition-all font-semibold">
        查看全部开源速递
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
